        "message": "=<h2>Book Outline Ready for Review</h2><p><strong>Title:</strong> {{ $json.title }}</p><p>An AI-generated outline is ready for your review in the Google Sheet.</p><p><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/{{ $env.GOOGLE_SHEET_ID }}\">Open Google Sheet</a></p><p>Instructions:</p><ul><li>Write \"no_notes_needed\" in column E to proceed with book generation</li><li>Write \"yes\" in column E and add feedback in column D to regenerate the outline</li></ul>"
